msgstr "Подписка на электронную почту"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:485
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:306
msgid ""
"Display a checkbox on the checkout page where customers can opt-in to "
"receive email marketing."
msgstr ""
"Отобразите флажок на странице оформления заказа, где клиенты могут "
"согласиться на получение email-маркетинга."

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:496
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Heads up: the <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> shortcode was not found "
"on the %1$scheckout page%2$s. The email optin checkbox is not yet supported "
"on the new block-based checkout."
msgstr ""
"Внимание: шорткод <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> не найден на странице "
"%1$sоформления%2$s. Чекбокс подписки на электронную почту пока не "
"поддерживается в новом блоковом оформлении."

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:501
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:313
msgid "Hide If Consented"
msgstr "Скрыть, если согласовано"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:502
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:314
msgid "Hide the email optin checkbox if the customer has previously opted in."
msgstr "Скрыть флажок подписки на электронную почту, если клиент ранее согласился."

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:508
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:320
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1210
msgid "Email Optin Message"
msgstr "Сообщение о подписке на электронную почту"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:509
#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:3723
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:247
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:321
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1211
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1292
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1599
msgid "I consent to receive marketing emails"
msgstr "Я согласен получать маркетинговые электронные письма"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:516
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:328
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1218
msgid "Email Optin Default"
msgstr "По умолчанию подписка на электронную почту"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:520
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:332
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1222
msgid "Checked"
msgstr "Отмечено"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:521
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:333
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1223
msgid "Un-Checked"
msgstr "Не отмечено"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:527
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:339
#: includes/integrations/give/class-give.php:1229
msgid "Email Optin Tags"
msgstr "Теги подписки на электронную почту"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:528
#: includes/integrations/edd/class-edd.php:340
msgid "Apply these tags to the customer when the email optin box is checked."
msgstr ""
"Примените эти теги к клиенту, когда флажок подписки на электронную почту "
