#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:537
msgid "WooCommerce Automatic Tagging"
msgstr "Автоматическая маркировка WooCommerce"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:544
msgid "Product Category Tagging"
msgstr "Маркировка по категориям продуктов"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:545
msgid "Generate and apply tags based on the category of every product purchased."
msgstr ""
"Создавайте и применяйте теги на основе категории каждого купленного "
