#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:551
msgid "Product Name Tagging"
msgstr "Маркировка по названию продукта"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:552
msgid "Generate and apply tags based on the name of every product purchased."
msgstr "Создавайте и применяйте теги на основе названия каждого купленного продукта."

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:558
msgid "Product SKU Tagging"
msgstr "Маркировка по SKU продукта"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:559
msgid "Generate and apply tags based on the SKU of every product purchased."
msgstr "Создавайте и применяйте теги на основе SKU каждого купленного продукта."

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:565
msgid "Tag Prefix"
msgstr "Префикс тега"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:566
msgid ""
"Enter a prefix (i.e. \"Purchased\") for any automatically-generated tags. "
"Use shortcode [status] to dynamically insert the order status."
msgstr ""
"Введите префикс (например, \"Куплено\") для любых автоматически "
"сгенерированных тегов. Используйте шорткод [status] для динамической "
"вставки статуса заказа."

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:574
msgid "WooCommerce Order Statuses"
msgstr "Статусы заказов WooCommerce"

#: includes/integrations/class-woocommerce.php:576
msgid ""
"<p>The settings here let you apply tags to a contact when an order status "
"is changed in WooCommerce.</p><p>This is useful if you're manually changing "
"order statuses, for example marking an order Completed after it's been "
